domain

Class Planet

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Planet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Relatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MilkyWayPlanet

    public abstract class Planet
extends java.lang.Object
implements Relatable
    This is an abstract Planet class. This class has protected fields-mass,diameter,revolutionPeriod and meanSurfaceTemperature. This class implements the Relatable Interface.It also provides an implementation for the isDiameterGreater and isMassSmaller methods,declared in that interface. In order to calculate the escape velocity field, an abstract escapeVelocity method is declared in this class.
    See Also:
    for implementation of escapeVelocity
